prompts.user_prompt_template:
Create a Listening Comprehension Exercise:

Level: {LEVEL}
Week: {WEEK}
Theme: {THEME}
Target WPM: {TARGET_WPM}
Duration: {DURATION_SECONDS} seconds
Vocabulary focus: {VOCAB_WORDS}

Provide:
1. transcript: a natural monologue or dialogue at the target WPM (include speaker labels if dialogue)
2. word_count: verify it matches target WPM × duration
3. questions: 8 questions [{type: literal/inference/detail, question, options: [4 choices], answer, timestamp_hint}]
4. new_vocabulary: 5 words from the transcript the learner should learn [{word, meaning_ar, context_sentence}]
5. accent_focus: one pronunciation pattern highlighted in this audio (linking, stress, schwa, etc.)
6. shadow_sentence: one sentence to shadow 5 times
7. answer_key: all correct answers with brief explanations

Return as JSON.
